full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/22/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE Processing Sheet Application or Petition Form No. File No. A28952345 DATA COLLECTION FOR ALIEN DOCUMENTATION, IDENTIFICATION & TELECOMMUNICATION SYSTEM (ADIT) Please print or type information requested below: COMPLETE NAME BIBI, AISHA COMPLETE MAILING ADDRESS (Include Zip Code) 13209 ANDY STREET CERRITOS, CAL 90701 MOTHER'S FIRST NAME BEGUM FATHER'S FIRST NAME FAKIR CITY/TOWN/VILLAGE OF BIRTH RAWALPINDI. PAKISTAN CITY OF RESIDENCE WHEN APPLYING FOR A VISA OR IMMIGRANT STATUS CERRITOS,CAL CITY OF DESTINATION AT TIME OF ORIGINAL ADMISSION CERRITOS, CAL LOCATION OF CONSULATE WHERE IMMIGRANT VISA OBTAINED (OR IMMIGRATION OFFICE WHERE ADJUSTED) Los ANGELES DATE OF BIRTH 5-31-1911 PORT OF ENTRY WHEN ADMITTED AS IMMIGRANT OR OFFICE WHERE ADJUSTED TO LAWFUL PERMANENT RESIDENT Los ANGELES SYMBOL ADMITTED UNDER (CLASSIFICATION) B-2 DATE ADMITTED OR ADJUSTED TO LAWFUL PERMANENT RESIDENT 9-9-87 COUNTRY OF BIRTH PAKISTAN CARD NUMBER TRANSACTION NUMBER This form may be overprinted or stamped to show instructions, items requested, items received, or other pertinent data which may facilitate processing. Keep this sheet on top of all material in file until initial decision is made. Form I-468 (ADIT) FPI-LOM (Rev. 11-1-70) 2-83 500 Tabs 5475
